snippet.title: Intro Cinematic for Fallen Frontier, by Moonshot Games
snippet.description:
This is the first cinematic of Fallen Frontier, a sidescrolling platform shooter created by Moonshot Games.
 
Art by Mike McCain, Christine Bian, and Ryan Demita.  Sound by Danny Dahlquist.  Music by Kevin MacLeod.  Written by Rob Stokes.
 
At the time this cinematic was created, the game was using the working title of Project Chimera.
